This development prompt provides a complete, actionable spec for building the Order / Transaction History page along with integrated Billing & Subscription Management and Subscription Management components. The design system, runtime safety rules, and project context are incorporated to ensure a production-ready implementation with robust null-safety, proper data handling, and a premium fintech UI.

